column5: Beauty fish Pete, congrats !!
I spy Squid in the Burlington post tonight. Winner of the catch of the week from Jakes Boathouse with his muskie!
Cool, maybe it won't only be the misty jrs asking for his autograph at the swill!  Mike
39 incher? LOL! Any pics?

Ah that's fantastic. You must be excited. I think it's great that a local bar runs a contest like this so us ameuter,honest fishingpersons can win prizes like this. Was it a free meal? I don't target musky, but would like to try one day. Any chance you could post a picture of the big Musky you caught to win Angler of the Week. Was it one that you caught last week on the Niagara?  How wonderful.
Congrats Squid!!
Congrats Pete! I must have missed the report wheres the pic?  Whopper
Congrats on the award.
All right!!!!  Great going Squid!  Congrats!  Were ya wearing your OFC clothing??? haha
Ok surprise surprise I had no idea.
That's great Peter.  Any chance we can get a link to the pic/article?  Joey
Congrats Pete.  Can't find a link so far Joey......
I can't find one either.
Peter, it was in yesterday Burlington Post, it says you won a $50.00 diner voucher and the picture is the one you just posted.  TH
cool
Congrats Pete. Nice fish also.
Congrats on the win Squid, Jakes has some fine food hope you enjoy.  Cheers, 1leg
I think you should share the prize with the net man / photographer
HAHAHAHAHA Lew, sure c'mon down to Burlington.
Nice fish Pete!  Whopper
Way to go Peter.  Regards, Sam
Cisco, it was a 48 incher actually.
Nice fish. That the one caught among several with 'Lew and his crew'  in the Kawarthas a month or so ago?
Yep.
WHO would have thought. Thought you where one of the poor lonely slobs, like the rest of us.
